## Migration Status

This is part of the OpenSSL to wolfSSL migration plan documented in:
`planning/06_openssl_to_wolfssl_migration.md`

### Migrated Components (Phase 3 COMPLETED)
| Component | Status |
|-----------|--------|
| syslogd (TLS + syslog-sign) | ✅ Using wolfSSL |
| ftp (SSL/TLS) | ✅ Using wolfSSL |
| httpd/bozohttpd (HTTPS) | ✅ Using wolfSSL |
| telnet/telnetd (SRA encryption) | ✅ Using wolfSSL |
| passwd (Kerberos UI) | ✅ Using wolfSSL |
| factor (BN factorization) | ✅ Using wolfSSL |
| BIND/named (DNSSEC) | ✅ Using wolfSSL |

### Testing Status (Phase 4 COMPLETED)
| Test Suite | Status | Location |
|------------|--------|----------|
| Unit tests | ✅ Done | tests/crypto/libcrypto/t_wolfssl.sh |
| Security tests | ✅ Done | tests/crypto/libcrypto/t_security.sh |
| Performance benchmarks | ✅ Done | tests/crypto/libcrypto/t_perf.sh |
| Compatibility tests | ✅ Done | tests/crypto/libcrypto/t_compat.sh |
| Integration tests | ✅ Done | tests/integration/ (6 scripts) |

### Remaining (Phase 5 — Cleanup)
